<P>THE VOYAGES AND ADVENTURES OF <HI>Captain</HI> ROBERT BOYLE, IN SEVERAL PARTS OF THE WORLD. INTERMIXED WITH THE STORY of Mrs. VILLARS, An ENGLISH LADY, with whom he made his surprising Escape from BARBARY. LIKEWISE INCLUDING The HISTORY of an ITALIAN CAPTIVE, and the LIFE of Don PEDRO AQUILIO, &amp;c. <HI>Full of various and amazing Turns of Fortune.</HI></P>
<P><HI>BOSTON:</HI> Printed and Sold by JOHN W. FOLSOM, No. 30, <HI>Union-Street</HI> near the <HI>Market,</HI> M,DCC,XCII.</P>
