<P>I had staid so long fixt at my peep-hole, that the old cu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="4 letters"> knocked at my door, which soon roused me from my plea<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="4 letters"> thoughts, and put me upon another task, which was, to dissemble I suffered him to knock twice or thrice before I let him in; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> last I opened the door when he had called to me to give me <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> know who it was: as soon as he was entered, I began to exclaim against him in a friendly manner; said I, You promised me yes|terday
