<P>In less than an hour, I saw the ladies coming down the walk; I ran immediately up to my peep-hole, and observed the mistress of my heart sauntering the way she used to go. As soon as I had discovered her in the walks again, I ran down, and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">ound a note in the room of mine; (at first I was uneasy, imagining she had not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> mine away) which contained to this purpose.</P>
